<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>4 Section Layout with Paragraphs</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
        }

        .box {
            padding: 20px;
            color: white;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .box1 { background-color: #ff6b6b; }
        .box2 { background-color: #4ecdc4; }
        .box3 { background-color: #1a535c; }
        .box4 { background-color: #ffa600; }

        h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="box box1">
        <h2>Section 1</h2>
        <p>This is the first section. It contains a paragraph describing the content of this area. You can add any text you like here.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box box2">
        <h2>Section 2</h2>
        <p>This is the second section. Each section has a different background color and its own paragraph content.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box box3">
        <h2>Section 3</h2>
        <p>This is the third section. The layout is divided into 2 rows and 2 columns using CSS Grid.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="box box4">
        <h2>Section 4</h2>
        <p>This is the fourth section. You can customize the text, colors, and styles as needed.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
